  "texts": [
    "A comparison of typical writing case corrections is shown in Table 5.",
    "This study utilizes visualization tools and detailed analysis of typical cases to clearly demonstrate the system's intervention effects.",
    "Figure 8 presents the grammatical error rate trends over 12 weeks for both the experimental and control groups.",
    "The experimental group (represented by the blue line) experienced a significant reduction in monthly errors, dropping from 28.7 to 6.3 (a 78.1% decrease).",
    "In contrast, the control group (yellow line) showed a more modest decrease, from 28.4 to 19.6 (a 31.0% reduction)."
  ]
}